Truth be told, I was never a fan of Quratulain Baloch ever since she performed with Noori. I always thought of her as a wannabe singer wayy outta noori's league. I mean they are exceptional. That was my perception until I saw this. And Omg, I have never been more thrilled to be wrong. And How happy am I to be this wrong. She's a massive bomb of excellent singing. Beautiful beautiful voice and what a command over every line of her. Just pure astonishing talent. Big Fan. 

Coke Studio Pakistan is wayy better than anything india's been upto recently. Hats off to you people. 
Love from India. 
Allah aap sab pe rehmat barsaye. Aameen.
